<subSubSection id="72A1650E0A110926379BFE78C5B7FE0E" pageId="1" pageNumber="423" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph id="3A0436850A110926379BFE78C5B7FE0E" blockId="1.[151,1437,392,527]" pageId="1" pageNumber="423">
<emphasis id="08CFEA970A110926379BFE78C74AFE6A" bold="true" box="[151,274,392,418]" pageId="1" pageNumber="423">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
This genus is similar to 
<taxonomicName id="FDBB4D060A1109263513FE78C566FE6B" authority="Ribaut, 1942" authorityName="Ribaut" authorityYear="1942" box="[543,830,392,419]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Phlogotettix" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="423" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="08CFEA970A1109263513FE78C4F0FE6A" box="[543,680,392,418]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="423">Phlogotettix</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="5E2A4B740A11092635A2FE78C566FE6B" author="Ribaut, H." box="[686,830,392,419]" pageId="1" pageNumber="423" pagination="259 - 270" refId="ref4512" refString="Ribaut, H. (1942) Demembrement des generes Athysanus Burm. et Thamnottetix Zett. [Homoptera-Jassidae]. Bulletin de la Societe d'Histoire Naturelle de Toulouse, 77, 259 - 270." type="journal article" year="1942">
Ribaut, 
<quantity id="FD439B600A110926340AFE79C566FE6B" box="[774,830,393,419]" metricMagnitude="1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.93268" pageId="1" pageNumber="423" unit="in" value="1942.0">1942</quantity>
</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
in appearance, but can be distinguished from the latter by the pygofer with an outer process arising from ventral submarginal ridge.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
